    "description": "Little Knight is a 2.5D party game that supports 2-4 players. Leverage your oversized weapon of choice to swing and fling yourself across various arenas and bring the fight to your friends and family. Master the goofy physics and show off your skills in frantic matches to try and come out on top. Collect and protect your horde of gold to win in the collection game mode or dominate your opponents in death match mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with up to four friends in local multiplayer</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135870/extras/277042e1ae6b05d20d287b51483abc74.poster.avif?t=1729680668\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135870/extras/277042e1ae6b05d20d287b51483abc74.webm?t=1729680668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135870/extras/277042e1ae6b05d20d287b51483abc74.mp4?t=1729680668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fling yourself around as you master the goofy physics movement</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135870/extras/2d2aef0da51599ce5358c3b6332c13dc.poster.avif?t=1729680668\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135870/extras/2d2aef0da51599ce5358c3b6332c13dc.webm?t=1729680668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135870/extras/2d2aef0da51599ce5358c3b6332c13dc.mp4?t=1729680668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose from four unique weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://